HEALTHY HORMONE SWAPS🤍

1. PERSONAL PRODUCTS:  These swaps with perfume or body cleanser are important to swap because of the phthalates (chemicals) in these products disrupt our endocrine system and long term create issues with healthy hormonal production. 
What I didn’t realize that something like one spray of perfume, a candle being on, or one cleanser we use on our body, we’re absorbing the chemicals or smelling it alllll day. This enters are system causing long term issues. 

2. CAFFEINE: caffeine on an empty stomach has proven to increase stress, cortisol production and limit appetite. With healthy hormones we want to invite our body to have a healthy appetite and not supress it. Also an increase of cortisol can limit your progesterone production. 

3. FOOD SWAPS: Eating carbs and sugar first thing in the morning can spike your insulin and cause chaos in the body.
